title: Pho Asian Noodle House
typeOfFood: Chinese, Thai, Fast food, Take-out, Asian, Vietnamese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Meat-based menu but some of the entrees come could be made with vegetable or tofu instead of meat, and there is also a list of vegetable dishes. Possibly the pho noodle soup and Vietnamese salad rolls can be requested vegan - ask. Atmosphere is fast-food. You order food at the cash register and dishes are brought to the table.
